","m":"faithful to one's vows"},{"d":"प्रथमम्","m":"in front"},{"d":"भर्तुः","m":"husband 's"},{"d":"मरणम्","m":"death"},{"d":"नार्याः","m":"O noble one"},{"d":"वैगुण्यम्","m":"fault"},{"d":"उच्यते","m":"is said to be"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"your"},{"d":"साधुवृत्तायाः","m":"of good conduct"},{"d":"मम","m":"I"},{"d":"अग्रतः","m":"in front"},{"d":"सम्वृत्तं","m":"virtuous one."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"दुःखाद्दुःखंप्रपन्नायामग्नायाश्शोकसागरे ।योहिमामुद्यतनिस्त्रातुंसोऽपित्वंविनिपातितः","trans":"\"I am in grief and filled with an ocean of sorrow. You who have come to save me and are also killed.\"","words":[{"d":"दुःखात्","m":"in grief"},{"d":"दुःखम्","m":"grief"},{"d":"प्रपन्नायाः","m":"reaching at"},{"d":"शोकसागरे","m":"ocean of sorrow"},{"d":"मग्नायाः","m":"filled"},{"d":"यः","m":"who"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"सोऽपि","m":"you are also"},{"d":"विनिपातितः","m":"are killed."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"साश्वश्रूर्ममकौसल्यात्वयापुत्रेणराघव: ।वत्सेनेवयथाधेनुर्विवत्सावत्सलाकृता","trans":"\"O Raghava! Even my motherinlaw Kausalya is separated from her dear son just as cow is separated from calf.\"","words":[{"d":"राघव","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"श्वश्रूः","m":"motherinlaw"},{"d":"कौसल्या","m":"Kausalya"},{"d":"वत्सला","m":"dear धेनुःयथा like a cow"},{"d":"पुत्रेण","m":"about son"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"likewise"},{"d":"वत्सेने","m":"about her dear son"},{"d":"विवत्साकृता","m":"is separated."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"आद्दिष्टंदीर्घमायुस्तेयैरचिन्त्यपराक्रम ।अनृतंवचनंतेषामल्पायुरपिराघव","trans":"\"O Raghava of incomprehensible valour! the words predicted by astrologers that your life is long is falsified. Your life has been short.\"","words":[{"d":"राघव","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"अचिन्त्यपराक्रम","m":"of incomprehensible valour"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"आयुः","m":"life"},{"d":"दीर्घम्","m":"long"},{"d":"उददिष्टम्","m":"predicted by astrologers"},{"d":"राघव","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"तेषाम्","m":"their"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"word"},{"d":"आनृतम्","m":"is falsified"},{"d":"अल्पायुः","m":"short life"