्म","m":"deed"},{"d":"कृता","m":"done"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"आत्मनः","m":"your own"},{"d":"पुण्यम्","m":"merit"},{"d":"राजर्षिवंशम्","m":"race of royal sages"},{"d":"समुपेक्षसे","m":"will be seeing."}]},{"v":20,"dev":"किंमांनप्रेक्षसेराजन् किंमांनप्रतिभाषसे ।बालांबाल्येनसम्प्राप्तांभार्यांमांसहचारिणीम्","trans":"\"O King! I have come to you while I was young. I am your companion and wife also. Why are you not seeing me? Why are you not talking to me?\"","words":[{"d":"राजन्","m":"O king!"},{"d":"बाल्येन","m":"in young age"},{"d":"बालाम्","m":"from a young age"},{"d":"सम्प्राप्ताम्","m":"have come to you"},{"d":"सहचारिणीम्","m":"companion"},{"d":"भार्याम्","m":"our wife also"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"नप्रेक्षसे","m":"you do not see"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"किंना","m":"why"},{"d":"मांप्रतिभाषसे","m":"you are not talking to me."}]},{"v":21,"dev":"संश्रुतंगृह्णतापाणिंचरिष्यामीतियत्त्वया ।स्मरतन्ममकाकुत्स्थनयमामपिदुःखिताम्","trans":"\"O Kakutstha! while you held my hand (at the time of marriage) you promised that you will be with me and likewise promised to take me, a (wretched one) with you to the other world. Remembering that I am sad.\"","words":[{"d":"काकुत्स्थ","m":"Kakutstha"},{"d":"पाणिम्","m":"hand"},{"d":"गृह्णता","m":"while held"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"चरिष्यामिइति","m":"will be with you"},{"d":"यत्","m":"likewise"},{"d":"संश्रुतम्","m":"promised"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"स्मरनाम","m":"remember"},{"d":"दुःखितम्","m":"sad"},{"d":"मामपि","m":"me too"},{"d":"नय","m":"such a one."}]},{"v":22,"dev":"कस्मान्मामपहायत्वंगतोगतिमतांवर ।अस्माल्लोकादमुंलोकंत्यक्त्वामामपिदुःखिताम्","trans":"\"O Jewel among those who attained good state! Why have you gone abandoning me dear? To which world have you gone from here? I am pained by your deserting me.\"","words":[{"d":"गतिमताम्","m":"jewel among those who have good status"},{"d":"वर","m":"O jewel"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"अपहाय","m":"abandoning"},{"d":"कस्मात्","m":"w